test_name: Living situation aligns with marital status
short_desc: If MARISTAT in (2,5) then LIVSITUA should not equal 2
full_desc: If Q3. MARISTAT (Marital status)= 2 or 5 (Widowed or Never married) then Q4. LIVSITUA (Living situation) should not equal 2 (Lives with spouse or partner)

test_name: Living situation aligns with marital status
short_desc: If MARISTAT in (1,6)  then LIVSITUA should equal 2
full_desc: If Q3. MARISTAT (Marital status) in (1,6) (Married or living as married) then Q4. LIVSITUA (Living situation) should equal 2 (Lives with spouse or partner)
test_logic: IF MARISTAT in (1,6) and LIVSITUA ne 2

test_name: Primary residence aligns with living situation
short_desc: If LIVSITUA=1 then RESIDENC should not equal 4
full_desc: If Q4. LIVSITUA (Living situation) =1 (Lives alone) then Q5. (Primary residence) should not equal 4 (skilled nursing facility, nursing home, hospital, or hospice)

test_name: Primary residence aligns with living situation
short_desc: If LIVSITUA=6 then RESIDENC should not equal 1
full_desc: If Q4. LIVSITUA (Living situation) =6 (Live in group home (e.g., assisted living, nursing home, convent)) then Q5. (Primary residence) should not equal 1 (Single– or multi–family private residence)

test_name: Primary residence aligns with living situation
short_desc: If LIVSITUA ne 6 then RESIDENC should not equal 3 or 4
full_desc: If Q4. LIVSITUA (Living situation) ne 6 (Live in group home (e.g., assisted living, nursing home, convent)) then Q5. RESIDENC (Primary residence) should not equal  3or 4 (Assisted living or skilled nursing facility, nursing home, hospital, or hospice)
test_logic: If LIVSITUA ne 6 and RESIDENC in (3,4)

short_desc: If MARISTAT[prev_vis] in (1,2,3,4) then MARISTAT should not equal 5
full_desc: If Q3. MARISTAT in (1,2,3,4) (Married, widowed, divorced, or separated) at previous visit then Q3. MARISTAT should not equal 5 (never married)

short_desc: IF MODEA2 !=0 and (INRELTO=1 and INLIVWTH=1), then LIVSITUA must equal 2
full_desc: IF Form A2 Q0d. MODEA2 !=0 (Form completed) and (Form A2, Q2. INRELTO (relationship to participant)=1 (spouse, partner, companion) and Form A2, Q4. INLIVWTH (lives with participant?)=1 (yes)), then Q4. LIVSITUA (participant's living situation) should equal 2 (lives with one other person: spouse or partner)
test_logic: IF MODEA2 !=0 and (INRELTO=1 and INLIVWTH=1) and LIVSITUA ne 2

short_desc: IF MODEA2 !=0 and (INRELTO=1 and INLIVWTH=0), then LIVSITUA cannot equal 2
full_desc: IF Form A2 Q0d. MODEA2 !=0 (Form completed) and (Form A2, Q2. INRELTO (relationship to participant)=1 (spouse, partner, companion) and Form A2, Q4. INLIVWTH (lives with participant?)=0 (no)), then Q4. LIVSITUA (participant's living situation) cannot equal 2 (lives with one other person: spouse or partner)
test_logic: IF MODEA2 !=0 and (INRELTO=1 and INLIVWTH=1) and LIVSITUA=2
